MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2019-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th February, 2019
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 15th February, 2019:
Shri Piyush Goyal relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs. Shri Piyush Goyal will continue to
hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Railways and the charge of the office of
the Minister of Coal;
i)
ii)
Shri Arun Jaitley relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister without Portfolio
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the charge of the
office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tel: 2379 2204
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
